you can

avoid manual async
avoid async.await
avoid context.assertTrue(res.failed()) and context.assertTrue(res.succeeded())
and use Assume.assume... inside an asyncAsserSuccess/asyncAssertFailure/verify block to properly skip a test so that JUnit reports it as skipped.

